    ↓ ↓ ↓ ↓ ↓ ↓ ↓ ↓ ↓ ↓ ↓ ↓ Radiação                |++++---++++| ←
    +++++++++     +++++++++ Máscara                 |++++---++++| ←
    ----------------------- Resist                  |++++---++++| ←
    ....................... Óxido Silício (SiO_3)   |++++---++++| ←
